people as prudish as those around your grandparents from whom you
claim &quot;there would certainly have been talk.&quot; Perhaps as a result, our
standards are different as far as gossip is concerned.

Whether or not Chaplin was within &quot;acceptably normal&quot; societal
standards is arguable. But it is an entirely separate issue from the
presumptive claim you try to tie to the situation with the
hypothetical you present. I have talked with both Rollie and Lita
directly. The picture of CC as the sole &quot;sexually...very agressive&quot;
